BitLife BR


BitLife BR is a video game that simulates a whole life, from birth to death and all the stages in between. Every decision you make throughout this life cycle has an impact on the development of your avatar's life. You may not notice this the first time you play, but it will become more and more obvious as you're reborn again and again.


The first thing you can read as soon as you're born is some basic information about your character: name, gender, country of birth, information about his or her parents, etc. The activities available to you during the first few years of your life are limited, which is pretty realistic, if you think about it. After all, until your avatar reaches adolescence, most of his or her decisions will be strongly influenced by the parents.


The BitLife BR interface consists almost exclusively of menus. All you can do while playing is make decisions. At times, you'll be presented with binary options, where you have to choose one thing or another. But, more often than not, the decisions you have to make are much more complex. This creates myriad possibilities, in which you can take different paths with each character.


BitLife BR is an excellent video game that manages to do something that seems impossible: compress a whole life onto your smartphone screen. It's very well-designed and perfectly adapted to mobile devices. The possibilities are almost endless in BitLife BR, and the results might just surprise you.


